Or wondering why you would need our services.Local businesses and companies will have many of their staff members tested prior to employments to check their suitability. Blood pressure and heart rate are measured by attaching a blood pressure cuff to the subject's arm, while respiration is measured with the help of respirometer, which is attached to the subject's chest.During a lie detector test electrodes will be placed on to the finger tips to analyse skin conductivity this is all done in a pain free manner.These three factors play a vital role.Our examiners undertake specialist training in order to be able to use the equiptment effectively and understand how the tests work.
